included.description: Research Assistant for Dr. Guy A Boy Dean of Human-Centered Design, Innovation and Art (SHCDIA) and Chief Scientist Of Human Centered Design at Kennedy Space Center,NASA. Actively participating in the design of an onboard weather situation awareness system for commercial aircraft cockpits. The goal of this new technology is to provide appropriate weather information to pilots, in the form of 3D visualization of weather and its evolution. I have accomplished an amazing piece of work in the representation of 3D clouds.
